{"tid":555287,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［城中大戰］亞洲大學排行榜2018 中大首躋身前10名","createTime":"2018-02-09T09:43:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-13T16:24:25.000Z","uid":106523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"48960a45c46c46137563537a1f4203c6cbcbe56f","tid":555287,"uid":106523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T09:43:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180207/57801088\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180207%2F57801088&d=iQT7bkje%2BHzlp0KayH313xFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=4f881da4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180207%2F57801088&h=1fb32cbd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180207/57801088</a><br />\n<br />\n泰晤士報高等教育昨公佈2018年亞洲大學排行榜，本港共有6間大學上榜，香港大學和香港科技大學分別位列第4和第5名。中文大學較去年上升4級首次躋身前10名，位列第7位。泰晤士報高等教育全球排名總編輯Phil Baty指，本港向來是亞洲大學排行榜中的「明星」，惟精英和二線大學之間的差距正在不斷擴大，隨著亞洲高等教育競爭加劇，本港排名較低的大學未來幾年或進一步下挫。<br />\n<br />\n今年本港大學在研究成果方面取得較高分數，在國際觀點方面評分很高；惟本港排名最差的3間大學因被引用文獻減少，全部排名均有所下跌。城市大學及理工大學同樣跌兩級，分別至第14及第19位，浸會大學則下降6位至第55位。排名第一的是新加坡國立大學，其次為清華大學和北京大學。<br />\n<br />\nPhil Baty指，本港僅擁有700萬人口，能在亞洲排名前60名大學中佔據6個位置是一項非凡成就。今年亞洲大學排行榜的主要趨勢是中國持續崛起，更在排行榜幾乎佔了五分之一，清華大學6年來首次成為中國排名第一的大學，中國的明星大學亦正不斷增加。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，韓國表現向來強勁，但今年明顯較遜色，台灣則因人口老化和高等教育供過於求正不斷遭受挫折，預期中國以外的國家需要加倍努力才能在激烈競爭中脫穎而出。<br />\n<br />\nShitty狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78a57fa1034b4e59e684a1f5e5f4a944f0f4c950","tid":555287,"uid":82720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T09:56:33.000Z","msg":"Shitty Poly BU<br />\n二線大學入面嘅三大"},{"pid":"188909961b608cf8606557c0e7647bae4460a323","tid":555287,"uid":87780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T10:23:27.000Z","msg":"排名最差的3間大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nlin u 呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e56039e85e92cc9e35dc97cd183ea30a06c12de1","tid":555287,"uid":106523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T11:02:58.000Z","msg":"做咩無shitty狗入黎數自己有咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咩QS排名出嘅時候唔係好撚串架咩"},{"pid":"ca879503571f9c317864ef47f103d13ce555edcb","tid":555287,"uid":3112,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T12:04:23.000Z","msg":"亞洲第一唔係東京大學已經可以直接ignore<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1094a060bb00f648997212813437d8b5c7178d21","tid":555287,"uid":28515,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T09:56:59.000Z","msg":"1.HKU UST CU<br />\n2.POLY BU EDU<br />\n3.LU CITY"},{"pid":"e2709345936b2fff67771851b9ddc13bb26f8899","tid":555287,"uid":135445,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"1094a060bb00f648997212813437d8b5c7178d21","tid":555287,"uid":28515,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T09:56:59.000Z","msg":"1.HKU UST CU<br />\n2.POLY BU EDU<br />\n3.LU CITY"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T09:58:31.000Z","msg":"我都幾肯定你條柒頭係讀緊教院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae03d8104fc39229530f139a1d305e7ba0dd977a","tid":555287,"uid":24160,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T05:36:23.000Z","msg":"浸會大學則下降6位至第55位。<br />\n<br />\n記得咪撚入BU<br />\nYear 1 就快啲Quit retake rejupas<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea05a720613ca0004f8bf60b1a22cbc1b8ce645d","tid":555287,"uid":139993,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T16:24:25.000Z","msg":"Bu仲有排跌<br />\n唔取消普通話試等收皮啦<br />\nBU唔係U"}]}